   Liu, Chang-Qiu, Guangxi Inst Bot, Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Reg, Guilin 541006, Peoples R China.
   Liu, Chang-Qiu, Chinese Acad Sci, Guilin 541006, Peoples R China.
   Sun, Hang, Chinese Acad Sci, Kunming Inst Bot, Key Lab Plant Divers \& Biogeog East Asia, Kunming 650201, Yunnan, Peoples R China.},
